## Architecture

```
Client                        Server
  │                              │
  ├── connect() ────────────────>│ authenticate (token/cookie)
  │                              │ join user-specific room
  │<──────────────────── accept  │
  │                              │
  ├── join("room:entity:123") ──>│ verify permission to join
  │                              │ add to room
  │<──────── room:joined         │
  │                              │
  ├── emit("entity:update") ───>│ validate payload
  │                              │ persist to database
  │                              │ broadcast to room
  │<──── "entity:updated" ───────│ (all room members receive)
  │                              │
  ├── heartbeat (ping/pong) ───>│ update last-seen timestamp
  │                              │
  ├── disconnect ───────────────>│ update presence to offline
  │                              │ notify relevant rooms
```

