## Room Management

### Room Naming Convention

```
Format: {type}:{identifier}

Examples:
  user:{userId}              - personal room (user-specific events)
  entity:{entityId}          - entity-scoped room (all subscribers)
  group:{groupId}            - group-wide broadcasts
  resource:{resourceId}      - live resource updates
  global:{channel}           - app-wide broadcasts
```

### Rules

- **Verify permission** before allowing a user to join any room
- **Leave rooms** when user navigates away from that context
- **Limit room subscriptions** - don't keep users in rooms they're not viewing
- **Server manages rooms** - clients request to join, server decides
- **Track who is in each room** server-side for event delivery guarantees

