## Presence System

```
Online Detection:
  1. User connects -> status: "online"
  2. Heartbeat every 30 seconds (client pings, server pongs)
  3. No heartbeat for 60 seconds -> status: "away"
  4. Socket disconnects -> status: "offline"
  5. Broadcast presence changes to relevant rooms (group, channel members)

Presence Data:
  {
    userId: string,
    status: "online" | "away" | "offline" | "do-not-disturb",
    lastSeen: Date,
    currentScreen: string | null,  // optional: current view identifier
  }
```

**Rules:**
- Update presence in database AND broadcast to rooms
- Don't broadcast every heartbeat - only broadcast STATUS CHANGES
- On reconnect, re-fetch presence for visible users (don't trust stale cache)
- Store last-seen timestamp for offline users if presence is relevant

